  "lernziele": "<p>The students are able to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>describe fundamental properties of standard and collaborative industrial robots</li>\n<li>elaborate robot based solutions for industrial applications</li>\n</ul>",
  "vorausgKenntnisse": "<ul>\n<li>Basic knowledge in automation / control engineering</li>\n<li>Fundamenta knowledge of linear algebra</li>\n<li>Solid command of the English language as the lectures are held in English</li>\n</ul>",
